{"tid":1134344,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"嚟緊考澤安 有咩要注意","createTime":"2019-05-01T17:23:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-05T13:58:39.000Z","uid":118501,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"39c546f5622f42834d83bbd703303c1870edc486","tid":1134344,"uid":118501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:23:57.000Z","msg":"嚟緊第二次考啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 抽到考澤安 請問有咩位特別要注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋通常會考邊條路線多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 求指導"},{"pid":"4088faed51b6eb4b0d8eadfcd6cf15d58b3f5b4b","tid":1134344,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd9dc4d1385306bf50c7d86871d122a5e35e7d7b","tid":1134344,"uid":118501,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4088faed51b6eb4b0d8eadfcd6cf15d58b3f5b4b","tid":1134344,"uid":72186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:24:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:26:35.000Z","msg":"巴打 考過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee15ca11cd063e13af00938aff7e0966a9d8d3c","tid":1134344,"uid":134375,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"通常考大埔道 其實冇乜特別 <br />\n我第一次考完油塘fail 抽到澤安覺得好輕鬆<br />\n小心閘口 小心大埔道落斜超速 過死車做足基本<br />\n過地盤會多泥頭車 行白田會有盲毛 自己執生<br />\n臨尾上大直路一開始係兩條線 之後二合為一 要打燈擰頭轉線<br />\n條路太闊都要行中間 係容易既 做足就得<br />\n加油💪🏼"},{"pid":"a36bce8be7c556467bad9429762569ea1ae37ae0","tid":1134344,"uid":118501,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6ee15ca11cd063e13af00938aff7e0966a9d8d3c","tid":1134344,"uid":134375,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"通常考大埔道 其實冇乜特別 <br />\n我第一次考完油塘fail 抽到澤安覺得好輕鬆<br />\n小心閘口 小心大埔道落斜超速 過死車做足基本<br />\n過地盤會多泥頭車 行白田會有盲毛 自己執生<br />\n臨尾上大直路一開始係兩條線 之後二合為一 要打燈擰頭轉線<br />\n條路太闊都要行中間 係容易既 做足就得<br />\n加油💪🏼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:36:11.000Z","msg":"唔該你啊巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我之前都係考油糖 好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72befcb43d1c55ece5dd15fa3453b40ee4f48f75","tid":1134344,"uid":68146,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T17:38:26.000Z","msg":"澤安最易<br />\n睇死車同停站車啦"},{"pid":"d5ffa09b1692d910742110dbc3fbe734714516fc","tid":1134344,"uid":11781,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:02:27.000Z","msg":"澤安真係最易 一般出去都係轉左行大埔道<br />\n其實最難都係小路出大路個位<br />\n睇定d先出 我果陣等左20分鐘都出唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過真係大路d車太多同完全唔讓<br />\n考官都知道我冇辦法 然後叫我架個車頭出去<br />\n之後pass左"},{"pid":"2cc4653319cd877726e5668dfcf0e27b8a66dca7","tid":1134344,"uid":53342,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:14:13.000Z","msg":"如果澤安都唔合格<br />\n真係要考慮一下。。。。唔好再考<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n提提你：<br />\n返試場上斜段路，小心小巴急停上客<br />\n祝你好運<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d23af9413d06803504e4807d2b20fd93a09607d","tid":1134344,"uid":22558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:18:05.000Z","msg":"通常考一線 打燈擰頭擰燈擰頭 好多死車"},{"pid":"34cff6e92b3541ade017ff900a15b6600b819797","tid":1134344,"uid":52215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:18:46.000Z","msg":"我好鐘意係白田村唔望路就咁過馬路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f612034a36a0d0a5b4276ed8cbfe9aa9e6564c5","tid":1134344,"uid":177736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T01:23:14.000Z","msg":"澤安 1  take pass <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最易考既路線"},{"pid":"0769b2d1ce8b2eb607beb0b12404f71c508c7a03","tid":1134344,"uid":118501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"34cff6e92b3541ade017f